LFo←{
     I←¯1 ⋄ MkV←{'FN',⍕I⊣(⊃I)+←1}         ⍝ New variable maker
     vis←{lft ast←⍵                       ⍝ Fn to visit each node
         (0=⍺⍺)∧'Function'≡⊃0 1⌷⍺:⍺(⍺⍺{     ⍝ Traverse Top-level Fn Nodes
             z←(⌽1 Kids ⍺),⊂lft MtAST         ⍝ Recur over children
